Comments.Message:
There is stray space character at the beginning of the file. Check attached screen shot.
Probably this xls file was sent to browser, and there is something that is echoing a space character before calling save method.
After deleting the space character, it opens fine (check attachment)

Can you check your script for space character being echoed, possibly before opening <?php tag, or maybe in some included file?

thank you very much. There was effectively a blank in an include file before <?php
